'''《恶战》'''（{{lang-en|''Hard Ball''}}）又名《谈判》（{{lang-en|''Negotiation''}}）<ref name="115alttitle">{{cite web|url=http://uk.tv.ign.com/objects/883/883326.html |title=Negotiation |accessdate=2013-08-08 |publisher=''IGN'' |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120209221316/http://uk.tv.ign.com/objects/883/883326.html |archivedate=2012-02-09 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name="115alttitle_2">{{cite web|url=http://www.wga.org/awards/awardssub.aspx?id=1516#tv |title=Writers Guild Awards |accessdate=2013-01-17 |publisher=''Writers Guild of America, West'' |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130117005725/http://www.wga.org/awards/awardssub.aspx?id=1516 |archivedate=2013-01-17 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>是[[美国|美国]][[情景喜剧|情景喜剧]]《[[我为喜剧狂|我为喜剧狂]]》[[我为喜剧狂_(第1季)|第1季]]的第15集，由助理[[制片人|制片人]]马特·哈伯德[[编剧|编剧]]，监督制片人唐·斯卡迪诺执导<ref name="sreen">{{cite web|url=http://www.screenrush.co.uk/television/television-813/season-2600/ |title=30 Rock: Episodes |publisher=Screenrush (AlloCiné) |accessdate=2013-07-28 |location=London |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120730001543/http://www.screenrush.co.uk/television/television-813/season-2600/ |archivedate=2012-07-30 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，2007年2月22日通过[[全国广播公司|全国广播公司]]在美国[[首演|首播]]。[[友情客串|客串出演]]这集的演员包括大卫·阿伦·伯施理、格里格·贝罗、[[卡特里娜·宝登|卡特里娜·宝登]]、凯文·布朗、格里兹·查普曼、瑞秋·德拉彻、凯斯·鲍威尔、朗尼·罗斯、格里高利·伍德尔，此外还有图克·卡尔森和克里斯·马修斯在节目中以自己的真实身份登场。

在这一集中，女演员简娜·玛隆妮（{{lang|en|Jenna Maroney}}，{{link-en|简·科拉克斯基|Jane Krakowski}}饰）在接受《[[美信|美信]]》杂志采访时由于听错了问题而导致其回答引起了争议。全国广播公司副总裁杰克·唐纳吉（{{lang|en|Jack Donaghy}}，[[亚历克·鲍德温|亚历克·鲍德温]]饰）开始就[[电视节目|电视节目]]《{{lang|en|TGS}}与崔西·乔丹》剧组成员乔什·吉拉德到期合约的续期展开谈判。电视台杂工跟班肯尼斯·帕塞尔（{{lang|en|Kenneth Parcell}}，[[杰克·麦克布瑞尔|杰克·麦克布瑞尔]]饰）成为男演员崔西·乔丹最新的一名随行人员。

==剧情==
为全国广播公司[[喜剧小品|喜剧小品]]《{{lang|en|TGS}}与崔西·乔丹》工作的乔什·吉拉德之前签订的工作[[合同|合同]]到期了，所以需要和副总裁杰克·唐纳吉商谈新的合同。后者希望通过这次谈判把对方的[[薪水|薪水]]拉低，从而节省一些资金，所以首席编剧丽兹·莱蒙（{{lang|en|Liz Lemon}}，[[蒂娜·菲|蒂娜·菲]]饰）提前告诉乔什要小心。由于乔什看起来好像生病了，她还去买了一些汤送给他，但却意外看到乔什和《[[每日秀|每日秀]]》的一位[[制片人|制片人]]进行商讨。丽兹大为光火，认为乔什脚踏两条船，于是决定在这场谈判中帮助杰克。乔什和经济人回到谈判桌前，相信和《每日秀》的协议十拿九稳了，但已经得知此事的杰克表示自己有能力让《每日秀》拒绝聘用他，这将导致乔什失去唯一的谈判[[筹码|筹码]]。然后他给出了与之前合同条款完全相同的新合约，乔什别无选择只能接受。丽兹仍然为乔什的背叛感到不快，要求乔什现场跳虫子舞。

女演员简娜在接受《美信》杂志采访时由于听错了对方的问题，导致其所做出的回答受到了误解，让人以为她“憎恨军人”，可实际上她说的是“讨厌剧团”。由此引来的争议让杰克不得不安排她上一次《{{link-en|与克里斯·马修斯的恶战|Hardball with Chris Matthews}}》节目，希望能化解之前的误会。没想到，简娜竟然把[[奥萨马·本·拉登|奥萨马·本·拉登]]和正参与[[民主党_(美国)|民主党]][[美国总统|总统]][[候选人|候选人]]提名角逐的时任[[联邦参议员|联邦参议员]][[贝拉克·奥巴马|贝拉克·奥巴马]]混为一谈。之后《{{lang|en|TGS}}与崔西·乔丹》的舞台上还意外出现了[[卐|卐]]，这更让情况雪上加霜。

崔西·乔丹为了表扬杂工跟班肯尼斯·帕塞尔对自己的好处，于是“批准”他加入自己的随从行列。但他意外发现另外两名随从格里兹·格里斯伍德和达特·康·斯莱特里一直在打[[篮球|篮球]]、玩《[[最后一战系列|最后一战系列]]》或是棋盘游戏时故意放水让自己赢，恼怒之下他“解雇”了两人，但肯尼斯独自作崔西的“随从”显然不是很够格。在电视台大楼下，崔西被一群正在大楼前抗议简娜言论的人挡住了去路，还以为自己被一群黑帮分子包围了，幸好格里兹和达特·康及时赶到，把崔西“救”了出来。

==制作==
曾长期和蒂娜·菲在全国广播公司[[喜剧小品|喜剧小品]]《[[周六夜现场|周六夜现场]]》中合作的瑞秋·德拉彻<ref>{{cite news|first=Christopher |last=Goodwin |url=http://www.theguardian.com/lifeandstyle/2008/may/11/women.television |title=And funny with it |accessdate=2013-07-31 |date=2008-05-11 |work=The Guardian |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090225222859/http://www.guardian.co.uk/lifeandstyle/2008/may/11/women.television |archivedate=2009-02-25 |deadurl=no }}</ref>本是扮演简娜·玛隆妮一角的初定人选，并已在节目起初拍摄的试播集中出演了这一角色<ref>{{cite news|first=Justin |last=Ravitz |title=Unemployment’s a Downer for ''SNL''-er Dratch |url=http://nymag.com/news/intelligencer/45792/ |publisher=''New York Magazine'' |date=2008-04-07 |accessdate=2013-07-28 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121013011052/http://nymag.com/news/intelligencer/45792/ |archivedate=2012-10-13 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref name="ew fine">{{cite news|first=Kristen |last=Baldwin |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20033897_2,00.html |title=One Fine Fey |accessdate=2013-07-31 |date=2007-04-10 |work=Entertainment Weekly |page=2 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121018010111/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C20033897_2%2C00.html |archivedate=2012-10-18 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。但到了2006年8月，执行制片人{{link-en|洛恩·迈克尔斯|Lorne Michaels}}宣布简娜一角将另选演员出演，但德拉彻还是会在之前的多集节目中以不同的身份登场。在最后播出的这集试播集中，她以《女生秀》养猫人的身份出镜<ref name="michaelsaboutdratch">{{cite news|first=Michael |last=Schneider |title=Inside Move: Dratch latched to multiple ''Rock'' roles |url=http://variety.com/2006/scene/news/inside-move-dratch-latched-to-multiple-rock-roles-1200342025/ |publisher=''Variety'' |date=2006-08-14 |accessdate=2013-07-28 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120516190758/http://www.variety.com/index.asp?layout=story&articleID=VR1117948462&cs=1 |archivedate=2012-05-16 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。同月晚些时候，全国广播公司宣布已由简·科拉克斯基取代德拉彻出演简娜一角<ref name="dratchout">{{cite news|url=http://www.zap2it.com/tv/news/zap-janekrakowskijoins30rock,0,1779072.story?coll=zap-tv-headlines |title='Ally' Cat Krakowski Joins '30 Rock' |accessdate=2013-07-28 |date=2006-08-17 |publisher=Zap2it |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120927030648/http://www.zap2it.com/tv/news/zap-janekrakowskijoins30rock%2C0%2C1779072.story?coll=zap-tv-headlines |archivedate=2012-09-27 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name="dratchout_2">{{cite news|first=Joel |last=Keller |title=Jane Krakowski added to ''30 Rock'' |url=http://www.aoltv.com/2006/08/17/jane-krakowski-added-to-30-rock/ |publisher=''AOL'' TV Squad |date=2008-08-17 |accessdate=2013-07-28 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120813214025/http://www.aoltv.com/2006/08/17/jane-krakowski-added-to-30-rock/ |deadurl=no |archivedate=2012-08-13 }}</ref><ref name="dratchout_3">{{cite news|first=Colin |last=Mahan |title=''30 Rock'' adds Jane Krakowski |url=http://www.tv.com/news/30-rock-adds-jane-krakowski--5917/ |publisher=TV.com |date=2006-08-16 |accessdate=2013-07-28 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080615234403/http://www.tv.com/ally-mcbeal/show/168/story/5917.htmlom_act%3Dconvert%26om_clk%3Dheadlinessh |archivedate=2008-06-15 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|first=Rebecca |last=Traister |url=http://www.salon.com/life/broadsheet/2010/04/14/tina_fey_backlash/ |title=The Tina Fey backlash |accessdate=2013-07-31 |date=2010-04-14 |publisher=Salon.com |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110820213538/http://www.salon.com/life/broadsheet/2010/04/14/tina_fey_backlash |archivedate=2011-08-20 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，此外德拉彻还将在之后播出的《[[C开头的那个词|C开头的那个词]]》中诠释这个养猫人角色<ref name="plotreference">{{cite episode |title=Pilot |episodelink=试播集 (我为喜剧狂) |series=30 Rock |credits=Writer: Tina Fey; Director: Adam Bernstein |network=NBC Universal |station=NBC |airdate=2006-10-11 |season=1 |number=1}}</ref>。在《[[后果_(我为喜剧狂)|后果]]》中，她扮演了一个名叫玛丽娅（{{lang|en|Maria}}）的女佣，丽兹发现她被锁在一艘游艇的衣柜里<ref name="theaftermath">{{cite episode |title=The Aftermath |series=30 Rock |serieslink=我为喜剧狂 |credits=Writer: Tina Fey; Director: Adam Bernstein |network=NBC Universal |station=NBC |airdate=2006-10-18 |season=1 |number=2}}</ref>。在《杰克遇上丹尼斯》里，德拉彻饰演了女演员[[伊丽莎白·泰勒|伊丽莎白·泰勒]]<ref>{{cite episode |title=Jack Meets Dennis |series=30 Rock |credits=Writer: Jack Burditt; Director: Juan J. Campanella |network=NBC Universal |station=NBC |airdate=2006-11-30 |season=1 |number=6}}</ref>。《[[崔西演柯南|崔西演柯南]]》中德拉彻出演的是崔西·乔丹出现幻觉时所看到的一个全身穿上臃肿蓝色服装的人，被称为“小蓝人”<ref name="tracydoesconan">{{cite episode |title=Tracy Does Conan|series=30 Rock |credits=Writer: Tina Fey; Director: Adam Bernstein |network[NBC Universal |station=NBC |airdate=2006-12-07 |season=1 |number=7}}</ref>。在《分手》中，她诠释了帕梅拉·斯缪，是崔西和图弗之间的一组灵敏度训练治疗师成员<ref name="break">{{cite web|url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0905647/ |title="30 Rock" The Break-Up (2006) |accessdate=2013-08-01 |publisher=IMDb |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120802103415/http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0905647/ |archivedate=2012-08-02 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。而到了《幼儿节目》中，德拉彻扮演了一位名叫格丽塔的女子，听说丽兹·莱蒙想怀个孩子后表示自己愿意做她的代孕母亲<ref name="baby show">{{cite episode |title=The Baby Show |series=30 Rock |credits=Writer: Jack Burditt; Director: Michael Engler |network=NBC Universal |station=NBC |airdate=2007-01-04 |season=1 |number=9}}</ref>，而到了《熬夜》里，她饰演的是杰克喝醉后叫来的一个妓女<ref>{{cite episode |title=Up All Night |series=30 Rock |credits=Writer: Tina Fey; Director: Michael Engler |network=NBC Universal |station=NBC |airdate=2007-02-08 |season=1 |number=13}}</ref>。在本集节目中，德拉彻诠释的是电视台大楼前引领抗议示威的一名领袖玛尔莎·布兰奇<ref name="theaftermath">{{cite episode |title=Hard Ball |series=30 Rock |credits=Writer: Matt Hubbard; Director: Don Scardino |network=NBC Universal |station=NBC |airdate=2007-02-22 |season=1 |number=15}}</ref>。《周六夜现场》还有其他多位演员也参加了《我为喜剧狂》的演出，包括[[弗莱德·阿米森|弗莱德·阿米森]]<ref name="somebody to love">{{cite news|first=Robert |last=Canning |url=http://uk.ign.com/articles/2007/11/16/30-rock-somebody-to-love-review |title=''30 Rock'': "Somebody to Love" Review |accessdate=2013-07-31 |publisher=IGN |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121022114115/http://www.ign.com/articles/2007/11/16/30-rock-somebody-to-love-review |archivedate=2012-10-22 |deadurl=no }}</ref>、[[克里斯汀·韦格|克里斯汀·韦格]]<ref name="somebody to love" />、{{link-en|威尔·福特|Will Forte}}<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.tvguide.com/episode-recaps/30-rock/february-1-2007-5916.aspx |first=Matt |last=Webb Mitovich |title=February 1, 2007: "It Feels Good to Laugh" |accessdate=2013-07-31 |date=2007-02-02 |work=TV Guide |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121019174231/http://www.tvguide.com/tvshows/30-rock/episode-12-season-1/281135 |archivedate=2012-10-19|deadurl=yes }}</ref>、{{link-en|莫莉·香侬|Molly Shannon}}<ref>{{cite episode |title=The Fighting Irish |series=30 Rock |credits=Writer: Jack Burditt; Director: Dennie Gordon |network=NBC Universal |station=NBC |airdate=2007-03-08 |season=1 |number=17}}</ref>、{{link-en|霍拉提奥·桑斯|Horatio Sanz}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tv.yahoo.com/30-rock/show/anna-howard-shaw-day/episode/229969/castcrew;_ylt=ApAQxiuPKcM.m1DE6hlJnR6xo9EF |title=30 Rock — Anna Howard Shaw Day |accessdate=2011-06-15 |publisher=Yahoo! TV |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110615061125/http://tv.yahoo.com/30-rock/show/anna-howard-shaw-day/episode/229969/castcrew%3B_ylt%3DApAQxiuPKcM.m1DE6hlJnR6xo9EF |archivedate=2011-06-15 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>、[[杰森·苏戴奇斯|杰森·苏戴奇斯]]、<ref name="sudeikis">{{cite news|first=Whitney|last=Matheson|title=A chat with ... ''30 Rock'' and ''SNL'' star Jason Sudeikis|url=http://content.usatoday.com/communities/popcandy/post/2007/04/159575/1|work=USA Today|date=2007-04-19|accessdate=2013-07-31|archive-date=2013-07-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130731101104/http://content.usatoday.com/communities/popcandy/post/2007/04/159575/1|dead-url=no}}</ref>、{{link-en|简·霍克斯|Jan Hooks}}<ref>{{cite news|first=Alan |last=Sepinwall |url=http://www.nj.com/entertainment/tv/index.ssf/2010/02/30_rock_verna_jan_hooks_guest-.html |title=30 Rock, 'Verna': Jan Hooks guest-stars |accessdate=2013-08-02 |date=2010-02-04 |work=The Star-Ledger |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121010221813/http://www.nj.com/entertainment/tv/index.ssf/2010/02/30_rock_verna_jan_hooks_guest-.html |archivedate=2012-10-10 |deadurl=no }}</ref>、[[克里斯·帕内尔|克里斯·帕内尔]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tv.yahoo.com/30-rock/show/the-baby-show/episode/115158/castcrew;_ylt=AvuPPAZBbLa7hQG9q4bBRVivo9EF |title=30 Rock — The Baby Show |accessdate=2010-04-21 |publisher=Yahoo! TV |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110615060804/http://tv.yahoo.com/30-rock/show/the-baby-show/episode/115158/castcrew%3B_ylt%3DAvuPPAZBbLa7hQG9q4bBRVivo9EF |archivedate=2011-06-15 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0931394/ |title=30 Rock The Baby Show (TV Episode 2007) |publisher=IMDb |accessdate=2013-08-02 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110909071159/http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0931394/ |archivedate=2011-09-09 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref name="baby show" /><ref name="parnell">{{cite news|first=Annie |last=Barrett |authorlink= |coauthors= |title=What ''SNL'' alums besides Chris Parnell should guest on ''30 Rock''? |url=http://popwatch.ew.com/2006/12/07/what_snl_alums_/ |work= |publisher=''Entertainment Weekly'' |date=2006-12-07 |accessdate=2013-08-01 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130608163606/http://popwatch.ew.com/2006/12/07/what_snl_alums_/ |archivedate=2013-06-08 |deadurl=no }}</ref>等。菲和崔西·摩根都曾是《周六夜现场》的主要演员<ref>{{cite news|url=http://uk.ign.com/articles/2006/10/18/ign-interview-30-rocks-tracy-morgan |title=IGN Interview: ''30 Rock''s Tracy Morgan |accessdate=2010-03-27 |last=Fickett |first=Travis |date=2006-10-17 |publisher=IGN |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130728020822/http://www.ign.com/articles/2006/10/18/ign-interview-30-rocks-tracy-morgan |archivedate=2013-07-28 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref name="tinafey_yahoo">{{cite web|url=http://tv.yahoo.com/person/tina-fey/biography.html |title=Tina Fey Biography |accessdate=2013-08-01 |last= |first= |coauthors= |date= |work= |publisher=''Yahoo!'' |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130801081437/http://tv.yahoo.com/person/tina-fey/biography.html |archivedate=2013-08-01 }}</ref>。亚历克·鲍德温也曾16次担任《周六夜现场》主持人，创下了该节目的最高纪录<ref name="alec_snl">{{cite episode |title=Alec Baldwin/Christina Aguilera |episodelink= |series=Saturday Night Live |serieslink=周六夜现场 |credits= |network=NBC Universal |station=NBC |airdate=2006-11-11 |season=32 |seriesno= |number=5 |minutes= }}</ref>。

==反响==
根据[[尼尔森收视率调查|尼尔森收视率调查]]的数据，《恶战》在美国首播时一共有460万户家庭观看，在18-49岁年龄段人群中收获了2.4 / 5的收视率。这意味着播出时全美所有该年龄段人仕中有2.4%观看这集节目，而当时有看电视的这一年龄段观众群里则有5%选择收看《恶战》<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/ratings/2007/02/27/nbc-ratings-results-for-the-week-of-feb-19-25-23731/20070227nbc04/ |title=Ratings - NBC Ratings Results for the Week of FeB_ 19-25 |publisher=The Futon Critic |accessdate=2013-08-08}}</ref><ref name="usratings">{{cite web |url=http://variety.com/2007/tv/news/season-high-for-grey-s-1117960045/ |title=Season high for 'Grey's' |accessdate=2013-08-08 |last=Kissell |first=Rick |date=2007-02-23 |publisher=''Variety'' |archive-date=2013-08-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130808051345/http://variety.com/2007/tv/news/season-high-for-grey-s-1117960045/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，与上一集《[[C开头的那个词|C开头的那个词]]》500万户家庭观看的成绩相比有所下降<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news.aspx?id=20070221nbc02|title=NBC Ratings Results For The Week Of Feb. 12-18|accessdate=2013-08-07|publisher=The Futon Critic|archive-date=2012-09-09|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6AXtZQTHH?url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news.aspx?id=20070221nbc02|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[美国在线|美国在线]]电视小队的朱丽亚·沃德（{{lang|en|Julia Ward}}）称赞这集的三条故事线索都非常优异，亚历克·鲍德温谈判的桥段因其对台词的精准把握而无比亮眼。沃德称鲍德温的出众表现并不局限在这一集中，正是这些表现为他赢得了一座[[金球奖|金球奖]]。她还表扬了《我为喜剧狂》在过去几个星期的时间里持续给出了让人满意的表现，已经给节目找到了恰当的节奏和步调<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.aoltv.com/2007/02/23/30-rock-hard-ball/ |title=''30 Rock'': Hard Ball - TV Squad |accessdate=2013-08-08 |author=Ward, Julia |date=2007-02-23 |publisher=TV Squad |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120829195855/http://www.aoltv.com/2007/02/23/30-rock-hard-ball/ |archivedate=2012-08-29 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。[[IGN|IGN]]网站的艾里克·戈德曼（{{lang|en|Eric Goldman}}）感觉《恶战》通过非常娴熟的技巧将3条故事线索像变戏法一般呈现出来，共同奉献了一出优异、实在的喜剧节目。他还认为《我为喜剧狂》剧组已经为简娜一角找到了更合适的角度，所以这一集里该角色也有着不错的表现。戈德曼还称赞了崔西和肯尼斯的故事桥段，认为这是“像样的一段”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://au.ign.com/articles/2007/02/23/30-rock-hard-ball-review |title=IGN: ''30 Rock'': "Hard Ball" Review |accessdate=2013-08-08 |author=Goldman, Eric |date=2007-02-23 |publisher=IGN |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121023052640/http://www.ign.com/articles/2007/02/23/30-rock-hard-ball-review |archivedate=2012-10-23 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

《恶战》一共获得了3个奖项提名，最终有一项获奖。蒂娜·菲的[[丈夫|丈夫]]{{link-en|杰夫·里士满|Jeff Richmond}}<ref name="tinafey_yahoo" />获得了一项[[艾美奖|艾美奖]]杰出原创主题音乐提名<ref name="07emmynoms">{{cite web|url=http://www.nyc.gov/html/film/html/news/080107_moftb_applauds_nyc.shtml |title=Mayor's Office of Film, Theatre & Broadcasting |accessdate=2012-10-20 |date=2007-08-01 |work=Mayor's Office of Film, Theatre & Broadcasting Official Website |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121020195545/http://www.nyc.gov/html/film/html/news/080107_moftb_applauds_nyc.shtml |archivedate=2012-10-20 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。编剧马特·哈伯德获得[[美国编剧工会奖|美国编剧工会奖]]最佳喜剧剧集提名<ref name="wga08noms">{{cite press release|title=Writers Guild Awards 2008 Nominations |publisher=''Writers Guild of America, West'' |url=http://www.wga.org/awards/awardssub.aspx?id=1516#tv |accessdate=2013-01-17 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130117005725/http://www.wga.org/awards/awardssub.aspx?id=1516 |archivedate=2013-01-17 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。《恶战》还获得了[[黄金时段艾美奖|黄金时段艾美奖]]杰出喜剧剧集奖提名<ref name="emmysubmits_1">{{cite web|url=http://theenvelope.latimes.com/awards/emmys/la-en-contentioncomedymay30,0,877718.story |title=In Contention: Comedy |accessdate=2013-08-08 |last=O'Neil |first=Tom |date=2007-05-30 |publisher=''Los Angeles Times'' |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121226004124/http://theenvelope.latimes.com/awards/emmys/la-en-contentioncomedymay30%2C0%2C877718.story |archivedate=2012-12-26 |deadurl=no }}</ref>并成功胜出<ref name="07emmywinners">{{cite press release|title=30 Rock |publisher=''Academy of Television Arts & Sciences'' |url=http://www.emmys.com/shows/30-rock |accessdate=2013-08-08 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130515050653/http://www.emmys.com/shows/30-rock |archivedate=2013-05-15 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

